To qualify for incentives under this section, an eligible company or its assignee shall:
Have an existing project under KRS 148.851 to 148.860 that was approved prior to June 26, 2009;
Invest a minimum of thirty million dollars ($30,000,000) in the expansion of the previously approved project;
Present one (1) or more new premier events on an annual basis at the legacy expansion project site. As used in this paragraph, "new premier event" means a premier event that was not presented at the existing project prior to approval of the legacy expansion project; and
Include a facility with a permanent seating capacity of sixty-five thousand (65,000) or more, where premier events will be held.
